*   **Property IDs:**  Use the EPLAN API documentation to find the correct property IDs for the connection definition point and cable properties you want to set.  Incorrect IDs will cause errors.
*   **Connection Point Logic:**  EPLAN uses connection point logic to determine how components connect.  Make sure your connection definition point symbol and cable function symbol have the correct connection point logic defined in the symbol editor.
